OL,6,FThe chief executive of Royal Mail,
OL,7,FSimon Thompson, is to step down from
OL,8,Fhis role, it has been announced.
OL,10,FMr Thompson, who has been chief
OL,11,Fexecutive of Royal Mail since 2021,
OL,12,Fsaid he believed it was "the right
OL,13,Ftime for the company to move forward
OL,14,Funder new leadership" after an
OL,15,Fagreement was struck between the
OL,16,Fcompany and union leaders last month.
